WEBVTT

00:00:06.233 --> 00:00:08.333
[SINGING IN JAPANESE]

00:01:33.100 --> 00:01:35.367
[♪♪♪]

00:01:44.500 --> 00:01:46.300
[ICHIGO PANTING]

00:01:56.166 --> 00:01:57.400
[GASPS]

00:01:58.100 --> 00:02:01.000
[GRUNTING]

00:02:12.467 --> 00:02:15.100
[PANTING]

00:02:21.767 --> 00:02:26.734
To have fought for so long and
still be standing is admirable.

00:02:26.734 --> 00:02:30.767
But the fact is, you
have yet to reach Bankai.

00:02:30.767 --> 00:02:33.667
Do you wish
to continue, Ichigo?

00:02:33.667 --> 00:02:36.734
ICHIGO:
Why do you even bother
asking such stupid questions?

00:02:36.734 --> 00:02:38.633
I have time no time for them.

00:02:38.633 --> 00:02:40.700
Come at me with
everything you've got.

00:02:40.700 --> 00:02:42.800
Very well.

00:02:42.800 --> 00:02:45.333
Let's do it, Ichigo.

00:02:45.333 --> 00:02:48.467
[SHOUTING]

00:02:52.333 --> 00:02:55.266
[GASPING]

00:02:55.266 --> 00:02:57.700
No.
Please stop, Lieutenant.

00:02:57.700 --> 00:02:59.767
Don't.
Please put away your sword.

00:02:59.767 --> 00:03:02.800
Lieutenant Abarai,
please don't do this.

00:03:02.800 --> 00:03:05.800
[MEN GROANING]

00:03:12.266 --> 00:03:13.433
[WHIMPERS]

00:03:17.233 --> 00:03:21.166
[GASPING]

00:03:21.166 --> 00:03:25.367
Unh. Renji,
why are you doing this?

00:03:27.066 --> 00:03:28.734
[♪♪♪]

00:03:35.033 --> 00:03:36.533
RENJI:
Just a little farther.

00:03:36.533 --> 00:03:40.500
Just a little while longer now.

00:03:40.500 --> 00:03:43.867
And I'll be there,
Rukia, to save you.

00:03:48.867 --> 00:03:51.800
I will never let
them execute you!

00:03:55.900 --> 00:03:57.900
[QUAKING]

00:03:59.133 --> 00:04:01.467
[GASPING]

00:04:10.133 --> 00:04:14.066
RENJI:
This spiritual pressure. Unh.

00:04:23.934 --> 00:04:26.800
Captain Kuchiki.

00:04:28.633 --> 00:04:30.934
BYAKUYA:
Where are you going, Renji?

00:04:30.934 --> 00:04:32.834
[GRUNTING]

00:04:36.233 --> 00:04:39.900
I'm going to save Rukia.

00:04:41.400 --> 00:04:43.367
No.

00:04:43.367 --> 00:04:45.266
I must!

00:04:48.166 --> 00:04:52.200
I assume that you're
refusing to let me pass.

00:04:54.333 --> 00:04:56.834
BYAKUYA:
I don't intend to repeat myself.

00:04:58.000 --> 00:05:00.667
[RENJI GASPS]

00:05:00.667 --> 00:05:03.767
[♪♪♪]

00:05:06.934 --> 00:05:09.000
[GROWLS]

00:05:12.734 --> 00:05:15.166
Senka.

00:05:15.166 --> 00:05:17.600
[♪♪♪]

00:05:19.266 --> 00:05:20.900
A special flash
step with a spin,

00:05:20.900 --> 00:05:22.467
where you move
behind your opponent,

00:05:22.467 --> 00:05:23.734
destroying
his soul chain

00:05:23.734 --> 00:05:28.266
and soul sleep at the same
time. Your favorite move.

00:05:28.266 --> 00:05:30.433
I've seen it countless times.

00:05:30.433 --> 00:05:34.367
Using simple logic,
my mind foresaw your attack.

00:05:34.367 --> 00:05:36.900
And now my body is fast
enough to counter you, too.

00:05:39.867 --> 00:05:43.800
Captain Kuchiki,
you can no longer destroy me

00:05:43.800 --> 00:05:45.433
with that sword.

00:05:45.433 --> 00:05:47.934
[♪♪♪]

00:05:47.934 --> 00:05:51.033
You talk as if
you've already won.

00:05:51.033 --> 00:05:52.000
[GASPS]

00:05:52.000 --> 00:05:55.100
BYAKUYA:
What makes you so confident?

00:05:55.100 --> 00:05:57.967
Don't tell me
that you believe that

00:05:57.967 --> 00:06:00.467
with your level of strength,
you can break my blade.

00:06:02.166 --> 00:06:03.266
[GASPING]

00:06:08.533 --> 00:06:10.166
Scatter.

00:06:10.166 --> 00:06:11.633
[GRUNTS]

00:06:15.567 --> 00:06:19.900
RENJI:
I told you, you can't kill me
with that sword anymore.

00:06:26.967 --> 00:06:30.266
Before I was promoted
to be your lieutenant,

00:06:30.266 --> 00:06:35.033
long before I even joined
13 Court Guard Squads,

00:06:35.033 --> 00:06:37.166
I was obsessed with one thing.

00:06:37.166 --> 00:06:40.000
The one man that
I wanted to surpass.

00:06:40.000 --> 00:06:44.834
That man is you,
Captain Kuchiki.

00:06:44.834 --> 00:06:48.300
You released your Zanpakuto
without calling its name.

00:06:48.300 --> 00:06:51.133
Does this mean that you--?

00:06:51.133 --> 00:06:55.600
And I will surpass you,
Captain Kuchiki.

00:06:55.600 --> 00:06:57.500
[♪♪♪]

00:07:00.867 --> 00:07:02.300
[GRUNTING]

00:07:05.734 --> 00:07:07.200
[SHOUTS]

00:07:08.100 --> 00:07:09.700
[GROANS]

00:07:11.500 --> 00:07:14.333
[GASPING]

00:07:14.333 --> 00:07:17.233
Your body has finally
reached its limits.

00:07:17.233 --> 00:07:20.767
And unfortunately,
you have run out of time.

00:07:20.767 --> 00:07:24.066
You may continue.
But if you choose to do so,

00:07:24.066 --> 00:07:26.867
you may die
before you reach Bankai.

00:07:26.867 --> 00:07:31.433
Do you still wish to carry
on with training, Ichigo?

00:07:31.433 --> 00:07:33.166
Bankai!

00:07:55.934 --> 00:07:57.667
[SHRIEKS]

00:07:58.600 --> 00:08:01.467
Hihio Zabimaru.

00:08:03.667 --> 00:08:05.900
Well, well.

00:08:05.900 --> 00:08:08.233
When did you
achieve Bankai?

00:08:08.233 --> 00:08:10.633
RENJI:
It figures
you didn't know,

00:08:10.633 --> 00:08:13.900
you who have no time for even
your own subordinates.

00:08:13.900 --> 00:08:15.633
I'll say it
once again.

00:08:15.633 --> 00:08:18.967
I'm going now
to save Rukia.

00:08:18.967 --> 00:08:22.200
I've already given
you my answer to that.

00:08:22.200 --> 00:08:24.033
RENJI:
Very well.

00:08:24.033 --> 00:08:26.100
If you won't let me pass...

00:08:28.433 --> 00:08:31.967
I'll kill you and step over
your corpse.

00:08:31.967 --> 00:08:33.734
Unlikely.

00:08:33.734 --> 00:08:36.400
With your ability,
you will find it impossible

00:08:36.400 --> 00:08:38.700
to make me
fall on even one knee.

00:08:40.700 --> 00:08:42.900
[SHOUTING]

00:08:43.867 --> 00:08:45.400
[SHRIEKS]

00:08:48.900 --> 00:08:51.033
[♪♪♪]

00:08:51.734 --> 00:08:52.867
[GRUNTING]

00:08:55.467 --> 00:08:57.233
[SHRIEKING]

00:09:27.433 --> 00:09:29.233
I see.

00:09:29.233 --> 00:09:32.834
Its power is truly
at the level of Bankai.

00:09:32.834 --> 00:09:37.133
Nonetheless,
it isn't enough.

00:09:37.133 --> 00:09:39.967
Scatter. Senbonzakura.

00:09:40.533 --> 00:09:42.033
[EXPLOSION]

00:09:51.467 --> 00:09:53.767
[♪♪♪]

00:10:05.433 --> 00:10:08.767
RENJI:
Senbonzakura, 1,000 blades,

00:10:08.767 --> 00:10:10.667
each too small
for the eye to see.

00:10:10.667 --> 00:10:14.166
When the blades fly, they
turn and reflect the sunlight,

00:10:14.166 --> 00:10:17.166
resembling 1,000
flower petals falling.

00:10:17.166 --> 00:10:18.900
I know it all too well.

00:10:18.900 --> 00:10:22.400
Unfortunately for you,
my sword's joints

00:10:22.400 --> 00:10:24.400
are connected
by my spirit energy.

00:10:24.400 --> 00:10:27.333
Your blades can't
cut through them.

00:10:27.333 --> 00:10:29.467
[♪♪♪]

00:10:29.467 --> 00:10:32.266
Just now, I disconnected
all of the joints.

00:10:32.266 --> 00:10:34.667
And then, I scattered
them deliberately

00:10:34.667 --> 00:10:38.700
in order to counter
your 1,000 blades.

00:10:38.700 --> 00:10:41.100
Does that
surprise you, Captain?

00:10:41.100 --> 00:10:45.333
I already told you, I can
see every one of your blades!

00:10:48.233 --> 00:10:50.700
[GRUNTS]

00:10:50.700 --> 00:10:52.000
RENJI:
What do you know?

00:10:52.000 --> 00:10:53.667
I got you
down on your knee.

00:10:53.667 --> 00:10:57.233
And now I'm going
to defeat you.

00:11:00.100 --> 00:11:02.900
I think it's time
to bring down the curtain

00:11:02.900 --> 00:11:06.433
on the struggle between us,
Byakuya Kuchiki.

00:11:14.166 --> 00:11:17.700
BYAKUYA:
You want to bring
down the curtain, huh?

00:11:20.567 --> 00:11:22.900
Very well.

00:11:22.900 --> 00:11:25.233
Then down
it's going to come.

00:11:25.233 --> 00:11:27.533
And the blade
of my sword will do it.

00:11:27.533 --> 00:11:28.934
Your sword!

00:11:28.934 --> 00:11:32.700
The sword that ends
this will be mine!

00:11:33.667 --> 00:11:34.834
[SHOUTS]

00:11:38.300 --> 00:11:40.133
[♪♪♪]

00:11:40.900 --> 00:11:42.834
Hado 33.

00:11:42.834 --> 00:11:43.800
[GRUNTS]

00:11:43.800 --> 00:11:45.467
Sokatsui.

00:11:52.867 --> 00:11:54.333
[RENJI GRUNTING]

00:11:54.333 --> 00:11:56.800
RENJI:
He's discarded the incantation.

00:11:56.800 --> 00:11:59.533
Can he really do this much
damage with a mid-level Kido

00:11:59.533 --> 00:12:02.667
without the spirit chant?

00:12:02.667 --> 00:12:04.300
RENJI:
I see you.

00:12:04.300 --> 00:12:05.934
Are you really foolish
enough to think

00:12:05.934 --> 00:12:08.166
you could hide from me
with such a simple trick?

00:12:08.166 --> 00:12:09.967
[♪♪♪]

00:12:18.000 --> 00:12:21.033
RENJI:
Damn it. I lost control.

00:12:21.033 --> 00:12:23.667
You're the foolish one,
Renji.

00:12:23.667 --> 00:12:25.367
I didn't release my Kido

00:12:25.367 --> 00:12:28.467
in order to obscure
my movements from you.

00:12:28.467 --> 00:12:31.500
I did it to interrupt
the rhythm of your Bankai.

00:12:32.100 --> 00:12:33.433
[GRUNTS]

00:12:33.433 --> 00:12:37.100
BYAKUYA:
The weakness of Bankai
lies in its sheer size

00:12:37.100 --> 00:12:39.834
and the overwhelming
power it releases.

00:12:39.834 --> 00:12:43.900
It goes far beyond the
abilities of any normal weapon.

00:12:43.900 --> 00:12:45.767
It is for that reason
that it is said,

00:12:45.767 --> 00:12:49.300
"One must train for 10 years
after learning Bankai

00:12:49.300 --> 00:12:52.900
in order to control it
completely."

00:12:52.900 --> 00:12:58.400
Renji, you are not ready
to use your Bankai in battle.

00:12:58.400 --> 00:13:00.133
[GRUNTING]

00:13:00.133 --> 00:13:02.367
I don't need
your lectures.

00:13:02.367 --> 00:13:04.200
I already knew
all of that

00:13:04.200 --> 00:13:07.100
when I came here
in the first place.

00:13:07.100 --> 00:13:10.400
Luckily for me, though,
my Zanpakuto is not only big,

00:13:10.400 --> 00:13:12.800
it's also strong enough
to lose some segments

00:13:12.800 --> 00:13:15.433
and still
keep on fighting!

00:13:15.433 --> 00:13:16.834
Bakudo 61.

00:13:16.834 --> 00:13:19.567
Rikujokoro.

00:13:19.567 --> 00:13:22.433
RENJI:
Aah. Damn.

00:13:22.433 --> 00:13:23.633
[♪♪♪]

00:13:23.633 --> 00:13:26.433
Put down your sword,
and you may yet live.

00:13:26.433 --> 00:13:30.333
Unless you still have some
hopeless idea about winning.

00:13:30.333 --> 00:13:33.300
[GRUNTING]

00:13:33.300 --> 00:13:38.266
In case you've forgotten, or if
perhaps it didn't occur to you,

00:13:38.266 --> 00:13:42.367
I'll remind you, Renji,
that I, too, have Bankai.

00:13:42.367 --> 00:13:43.900
[♪♪♪]

00:13:43.900 --> 00:13:44.934
[GASPS]

00:13:47.900 --> 00:13:49.834
BYAKUYA:
Bankai.

00:13:55.266 --> 00:13:57.367
[GASPING]

00:13:57.367 --> 00:13:59.800
[♪♪♪]

00:14:17.500 --> 00:14:19.367
[GASPING]

00:14:20.500 --> 00:14:21.967
Scatter.

00:14:21.967 --> 00:14:24.166
Senbonzakura Kageyoshi.

00:14:45.834 --> 00:14:49.233
[GASPING]

00:15:04.934 --> 00:15:08.200
BYAKUYA:
A thousand blades
rise from the ground.

00:15:08.200 --> 00:15:09.233
With their scattering,

00:15:09.233 --> 00:15:11.700
infinitely
more blades then rise.

00:15:11.700 --> 00:15:13.734
Impossible to know
their numbers.

00:15:13.734 --> 00:15:17.967
Impossible to even read their
path, much less avoid them.

00:15:17.967 --> 00:15:22.200
Nothing to do but watch,
as one watches the wind pass,

00:15:22.200 --> 00:15:26.033
and wait for the blades
to pass through you.

00:15:26.033 --> 00:15:29.367
One can do nothing
but stand there, frozen,

00:15:29.367 --> 00:15:33.500
and then be swept away
from this world.

00:15:33.500 --> 00:15:36.934
Shall I tell you the
difference between you and I?

00:15:39.400 --> 00:15:41.800
It's class.

00:15:41.800 --> 00:15:44.333
It's like the story
of the monkey

00:15:44.333 --> 00:15:46.533
trying to capture
the moon.

00:15:46.533 --> 00:15:49.100
No matter how
he struggles,

00:15:49.100 --> 00:15:52.467
it's just the moon's reflection
on the water he sees.

00:15:52.467 --> 00:15:54.700
So he only sinks
into the water.

00:15:54.700 --> 00:15:57.233
Time after time,
the monkey sinks.

00:15:57.233 --> 00:16:02.867
Your fang could never hope
to actually reach me. Never.

00:16:05.100 --> 00:16:08.734
But be proud, proud of the fact
that you were failed

00:16:08.734 --> 00:16:12.400
by this blade, yet you
still retain a human form.

00:16:15.233 --> 00:16:17.400
[♪♪♪]

00:16:17.400 --> 00:16:20.200
[GASPING]

00:16:25.633 --> 00:16:28.266
BYAKUYA:
So you can
still breathe.

00:16:28.266 --> 00:16:31.700
[CONTINUED GASPING]

00:16:31.700 --> 00:16:33.266
BYAKUYA:
Do not move.

00:16:33.266 --> 00:16:35.133
You will only
hasten your death.

00:16:48.734 --> 00:16:51.633
RENJI [GASPING]:
It's not over.

00:16:51.633 --> 00:16:53.900
It's
not over.

00:16:53.900 --> 00:16:57.133
I can still fight.

00:16:57.133 --> 00:16:58.800
Didn't you hear me?

00:16:58.800 --> 00:17:02.834
I told you not to move.

00:17:02.834 --> 00:17:04.900
[SHOUTS]

00:17:08.500 --> 00:17:09.734
Huh?

00:17:09.734 --> 00:17:12.433
[SHOUTS]

00:17:12.433 --> 00:17:14.633
[CONTINUES GASPING]

00:17:14.633 --> 00:17:16.667
I must compliment you.

00:17:16.667 --> 00:17:20.367
Though you received
my Bankai, you still live

00:17:20.367 --> 00:17:22.767
and even wish
to continue fighting.

00:17:22.767 --> 00:17:29.000
However, do not try
to stand up again.

00:17:29.000 --> 00:17:32.533
If you do, this blade will
carve you into pieces.

00:17:32.533 --> 00:17:33.667
That I promise you.

00:17:34.467 --> 00:17:36.867
[CONTINUES GASPING]

00:17:36.867 --> 00:17:41.300
BYAKUYA:
You must have noticed by now
that your Bankai is gone.

00:17:41.300 --> 00:17:43.000
When one's Bankai
disappears

00:17:43.000 --> 00:17:45.800
without the permission
of its master,

00:17:45.800 --> 00:17:49.333
it means that the master's time
of death draws near.

00:17:49.333 --> 00:17:52.767
Soon enough, now, you
will begin to fade away.

00:17:52.767 --> 00:17:55.834
So I shall ask you
this one more time.

00:17:55.834 --> 00:17:59.633
Will you at long last give up
this foolish dream of yours,

00:17:59.633 --> 00:18:01.533
of saving Rukia?

00:18:04.533 --> 00:18:06.066
[♪♪♪]

00:18:06.066 --> 00:18:09.633
RENJI:
I-- I can't breathe.

00:18:09.633 --> 00:18:14.867
His spiritual pressure
alone is tearing me apart.

00:18:14.867 --> 00:18:18.100
I can't even
move my fingers.

00:18:21.700 --> 00:18:24.000
In the end, this man and I,

00:18:24.000 --> 00:18:28.400
we're too far apart...
after all.

00:18:28.400 --> 00:18:31.000
[GASPING]

00:18:31.934 --> 00:18:33.400
[♪♪♪]

00:18:37.166 --> 00:18:41.200
Can you still stand
and continue, Ichigo?

00:18:41.200 --> 00:18:42.934
[GASPS]

00:18:42.934 --> 00:18:45.066
[CHUCKLES]

00:18:46.967 --> 00:18:51.900
Heh, heh.
Of course I can.

00:18:51.900 --> 00:18:53.767
Hm?

00:18:53.767 --> 00:18:55.734
ICHIGO:
Because I swore.

00:18:55.734 --> 00:18:58.867
RENJI:
I swore that I'd save her.

00:18:58.867 --> 00:19:01.100
You swore this?

00:19:01.100 --> 00:19:04.934
You swore
it to whom?

00:19:04.934 --> 00:19:06.800
RENJI:
No one.

00:19:06.800 --> 00:19:09.800
ICHIGO:
I just swore it.

00:19:09.800 --> 00:19:12.900
I just swore it!

00:19:12.900 --> 00:19:15.567
RENJI: To myself!
ICHIGO: To myself!

00:19:18.166 --> 00:19:20.767
[♪♪♪]

00:19:31.533 --> 00:19:35.367
IKKAKU:
You want to be stronger
than Byakuya Kuchiki?

00:19:35.367 --> 00:19:37.767
You've set yourself
an impossible goal.

00:19:37.767 --> 00:19:42.834
IZURU:
You'd better just stay
away from her from now on.

00:19:42.834 --> 00:19:45.266
She understands
the situation, too.

00:19:45.266 --> 00:19:48.567
She knows that she's
different from the rest of us.

00:19:51.100 --> 00:19:54.300
YUMICHIKA:
It's for your own good.
And for hers, too.

00:19:54.300 --> 00:19:58.166
It's a shame, but, well,
it's kind of complicated.

00:19:58.166 --> 00:20:02.133
But it's always a lot easier
to let something fall apart

00:20:02.133 --> 00:20:04.867
than it is to try
to hold it together.

00:20:04.867 --> 00:20:08.667
[♪♪♪]

00:20:08.667 --> 00:20:11.667
[SCREAMING]

00:20:49.533 --> 00:20:51.800
[GASPING]

00:20:51.800 --> 00:20:53.967
Damn it.

00:20:55.467 --> 00:20:57.300
[GRUNTS]

00:21:06.834 --> 00:21:08.533
Congratulations.

00:21:10.767 --> 00:21:12.900
Very admirable.

00:21:12.900 --> 00:21:16.433
That time, your fang
definitely reached me.

00:21:17.834 --> 00:21:20.166
[♪♪♪]

00:21:34.834 --> 00:21:36.233
Renji.

00:21:37.567 --> 00:21:38.533
[GASPS]

00:21:38.533 --> 00:21:40.100
Impossible.

00:21:40.100 --> 00:21:42.700
Until just now when it
faded, it was so powerful,

00:21:42.700 --> 00:21:45.567
I couldn't tell whose
spiritual pressure that was.

00:21:45.567 --> 00:21:47.467
It was Renji.

00:21:47.467 --> 00:21:50.400
Renji! Why--
Why'd you do it?

00:21:50.400 --> 00:21:51.500
Renji!

00:21:56.300 --> 00:21:57.934
Huh?

00:22:03.967 --> 00:22:05.900
[GASPS]

